snippet.title: Amber Heard Admits to Hitting Johnny Depp in Audio Recording
snippet.description:
JOHNNY DEPP: #AmberHeard took the stand in the #JohnnyDepp libel case against The Sun tabloid. Depp claims that he's lost work after the British paper said he was a "wife-beater".

Watch #CourtTV LIVE tonight at 8/7c. court.tv/live
